snippet.title: Tequila & Boom Boom gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Tequila & Boom Boom, Dos PC game produced by Dynabyte in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/tequila-boom-boom/15750/
Tequila & Boom Boom is a nice, classic, where it can be an adventure in the Wild West, with many interesting animations.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Nicky Boom - https://youtu.be/9aU-UavSp5k
